00:40:49.018 --> 00:40:52.414
humans could create a
closed biosphere that would

00:40:52.414 --> 00:40:53.646
sustain human life.

00:40:53.646 --> 00:40:57.292
And, it was a miserable
failure, which is sad because

00:40:57.292 --> 00:40:59.998
