and has since

00:40:59.998 --> 00:41:04.664
been taken over by Columbia
University to use it as an

00:41:04.664 --> 00:41:06.474
experimental facility.

00:41:06.474 --> 00:41:09.599
But the one thing that they
learned,

00:41:09.599 --> 00:41:11.181
here's what happened.

00:41:11.181 --> 00:41:12.914
They put the people in.

00:41:12.914 --> 00:41:16.328
