00:41:21.375 --> 00:41:23.822
Oxygen levels steadily went
down.

00:41:23.822 --> 00:41:27.353
And the reason
for that, they learned later,

00:41:27.353 --> 00:41:30.398
was that they had put way too
much rich

00:41:30.398 --> 00:41:32.125
soil in the system.

00:41:32.125 --> 00:41:35.306
So, the bacteria in the soil
were

00:41:35.306 --> 00:41:38.602
sucking the oxygen out of the
atmosphere.

00:41:38.602 --> 00:41:41.867
And they were
subsidizing the system with

00:41:41.867 --> 00:41:44.536
