the same amount of,

00:41:55.020 --> 00:41:57.922
if this oxygen is coming from
photosynthesis,

00:41:57.922 --> 00:42:00.732
you
should see the same amount of

00:42:00.732 --> 00:42:03.000
CO2 coming into the system.

00:42:03.000 --> 00:42:06.958
And you should see an increase
in CO2 in the atmosphere.

00:42:06.958 --> 00:42:08.238
And they
didn't.

00:42:08.238 --> 00:42:11.172
In other words,
they saw oxygen going down,

00:42:11.172 --> 00:42:14.107
but they didn't
see surplus CO2 in the

00:42:14.107 --> 00:42:14.911
