00:42:14.911 --> 00:42:18.654
And it took a bright graduate
student from Columbia

00:42:18.654 --> 00:42:22.000
University to go in there and
figure out what was

00:42:22.000 --> 00:42:22.657
going on.

00:42:22.657 --> 00:42:26.311
And it turned out that,
so why didn't CO2 increase?

00:42:26.311 --> 00:42:28.549
